				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The 27C160 is a 16-bit ROM; its address lines specify an address in 16-bit words.<br />The CX4 wants to talk to an 8-bit ROM.<br /><br />Therefore, tie /BYTE low, and connect <br />ROM A-1 to CX4 A0<br />ROM A0 to CX4 A1<br />ROM A1 to CX4 A2<br />and so on up.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

